{"tid":2462430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"第2針開打︱市民無懼事故照打科興 家庭主婦：我信得過政府","createTime":"2021-03-26T04:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T04:02:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb539f87808bff0cea2820594be30e217179270c","tid":2462430,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"家庭主婦唐女士表示接種第二劑疫苗的過程順利，工作人員的解釋和指引十分清楚。她指完成接種第一劑疫苗後未有不良反應，「冇嘢喎，好似以前打預防針咁樣囉...都冇咩反應。」懷疑因接種科興疫苗所致的事故不斷發生，惟唐女士未有因此而考慮停打第二針或轉而接種復必泰疫苗，「我又冇擔心，因為我信得過政府囉。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OVSBktOicn9Wi3h0TLpcfx_7kfE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCELXJNC7RDYLFNZNMXLQVCWEU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOVSBktOicn9Wi3h0TLpcfx_7kfE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCELXJNC7RDYLFNZNMXLQVCWEU.JPG&h=d7cd3ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唐女士<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/J4JQDX2VLJFV3JZF4JXBJYKQ2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210326%2FJ4JQDX2VLJFV3JZF4JXBJYKQ2Y%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=ad13caee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210326%2FJ4JQDX2VLJFV3JZF4JXBJYKQ2Y%2F&h=040a8eb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/J4JQDX2VLJFV3JZF4JXBJYKQ2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"417f1503b95e674dfe6145f133e179873b36149d","tid":2462430,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"信就一定冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}